title: Katherine Webb posts sizzling bikini selfies | Daily Mail Online
text: show ad One hot mama! Katherine Webb posts sizzling bikini selfies on her Instagram while enjoying a 'mommy and baby' day out at an Alabama beach The 27-year-old former beauty queen celebrated President's Day weekend by taking her nine-month-old son Tripp on a day trip to Orange Beach, Alabama Katherine took to Instagram on Sunday to share a few bikini selfies, as well as an adorable photo of Tripp playing in the sand On Saturday, the mother-of-one took Tripp to see his dad, Cincinnati Bengals quarterback AJ McCarron, ride a float in a Mardi Gras parade Published: 15:01 GMT, 20 February 2017 | Updated: 15:01 GMT, 20 February 2017 103 shares
